  ['to_20a_20strong_20voided_20state_20strong_20due_20to_20different_20voiding_20conditions_112',['&lt;strong&gt;Voidable DD-MPBs&lt;/strong&gt; are MPBs whose distinctive characteristic is that implement non-latching switches that while being pressed their state might change from &lt;strong&gt;On State&lt;/strong&gt; to a &lt;strong&gt;Voided state&lt;/strong&gt; due to different voiding conditions.',['../index.html#voidable-dd-mpbs-are-mpbs-whose-distinctive-characteristic-is-that-implement-non-latching-switches-that-while-being-pressed-their-state-might-change-from-on-state-to-a-voided-state-due-to-different-voiding-conditions',1,'']]],
  ['to_20be_20executed_20when_20the_20switch_20enters_20the_20strong_20on_20state_20strong_20are_20started_20that_20means_20setting_20the_20strong_20ison_20strong_20attribute_20flag_20and_20calling_20the_20strong_20fnwhntrnon_20strong_20function_20the_20driving_20concept_20is_20to_20instantiate_20a_20mpbttn_20that_20generates_20only_20one_20possible_20strong_20ison_20strong_20attribute_20flag_20true_20readout_20and_20the_20associated_20function_20execution_20just_20like_20a_20single_20shot_20trigger_113',['The &lt;strong&gt;Single Service Voidable Momentary Push Button&lt;/strong&gt; keeps the &lt;strong&gt;On state&lt;/strong&gt; since the moment the signal is stable (debounce &amp; delay process) and until the moment the provided mechanisms implemented to be executed when the switch enters the &lt;strong&gt;On State&lt;/strong&gt; are started, that means setting the &lt;strong&gt;isOn&lt;/strong&gt; attribute flag and calling the &lt;strong&gt;fnWhnTrnOn&lt;/strong&gt; function. The driving concept is to instantiate a MPBttn that generates only one possible &lt;strong&gt;isOn&lt;/strong&gt; attribute flag true readout and the associated function execution, just like a single shot trigger.',['../index.html#the-single-service-voidable-momentary-push-button-keeps-the-on-state-since-the-moment-the-signal-is-stable-debounce--delay-process-and-until-the-moment-the-provided-mechanisms-implemented-to-be-executed-when-the-switch-enters-the-on-state-are-started-that-means-setting-the-ison-attribute-flag-and-calling-the-fnwhntrnon-function-the-driving-concept-is-to-instantiate-a-mpbttn-that-generates-only-one-possible-ison-attribute-flag-true-readout-and-the-associated-function-execution-just-like-a-single-shot-trigger',1,'']]],
  ['to_20different_20voiding_20conditions_114',['&lt;strong&gt;Voidable DD-MPBs&lt;/strong&gt; are MPBs whose distinctive characteristic is that implement non-latching switches that while being pressed their state might change from &lt;strong&gt;On State&lt;/strong&gt; to a &lt;strong&gt;Voided state&lt;/strong&gt; due to different voiding conditions.',['../index.html#voidable-dd-mpbs-are-mpbs-whose-distinctive-characteristic-is-that-implement-non-latching-switches-that-while-being-pressed-their-state-might-change-from-on-state-to-a-voided-state-due-to-different-voiding-conditions',1,'']]],
  ['to_20give_20a_20warning_20when_20the_20service_20time_20is_20close_20to_20the_20end_20and_20the_20possibility_20to_20set_20a_20third_20signal_20on_20while_20the_20switch_20is_20off_115',['The &lt;strong&gt;Hinted Timer Latched&lt;/strong&gt;, or &lt;strong&gt;Staircase Timer Switch&lt;/strong&gt;, keeps the ON state since the moment the signal is debounced, and keeps the state during a set time, has the capability to give a warning when the service time is close to the end and the possibility to set a third signal ON while the switch is off.',['../index.html#the-hinted-timer-latched-or-staircase-timer-switch-keeps-the-on-state-since-the-moment-the-signal-is-debounced-and-keeps-the-state-during-a-set-time-has-the-capability-to-give-a-warning-when-the-service-time-is-close-to-the-end-and-the-possibility-to-set-a-third-signal-on-while-the-switch-is-off',1,'']]],
  ['to_20go_20back_20to_20the_20strong_20off_20state_20strong_116',['&lt;strong&gt;Latched DD-MPBs&lt;/strong&gt; are MPBs whose distinctive characteristic is that models switches that keep the ON state since the moment the input signal is stable (debouncing + Delay process), and keeps the ON state after the MPB is released and until an event un-latches them, setting them free to go back to the &lt;strong&gt;Off State&lt;/strong&gt;.',['../index.html#latched-dd-mpbs-are-mpbs-whose-distinctive-characteristic-is-that-models-switches-that-keep-the-on-state-since-the-moment-the-input-signal-is-stable-debouncing--delay-process-and-keeps-the-on-state-after-the-mpb-is-released-and-until-an-event-un-latches-them-setting-them-free-to-go-back-to-the-off-state',1,'']]],
  ['to_20instantiate_20a_20mpbttn_20that_20generates_20only_20one_20possible_20strong_20ison_20strong_20attribute_20flag_20true_20readout_20and_20the_20associated_20function_20execution_20just_20like_20a_20single_20shot_20trigger_117',['The &lt;strong&gt;Single Service Voidable Momentary Push Button&lt;/strong&gt; keeps the &lt;strong&gt;On state&lt;/strong&gt; since the moment the signal is stable (debounce &amp; delay process) and until the moment the provided mechanisms implemented to be executed when the switch enters the &lt;strong&gt;On State&lt;/strong&gt; are started, that means setting the &lt;strong&gt;isOn&lt;/strong&gt; attribute flag and calling the &lt;strong&gt;fnWhnTrnOn&lt;/strong&gt; function. The driving concept is to instantiate a MPBttn that generates only one possible &lt;strong&gt;isOn&lt;/strong&gt; attribute flag true readout and the associated function execution, just like a single shot trigger.',['../index.html#the-single-service-voidable-momentary-push-button-keeps-the-on-state-since-the-moment-the-signal-is-stable-debounce--delay-process-and-until-the-moment-the-provided-mechanisms-implemented-to-be-executed-when-the-switch-enters-the-on-state-are-started-that-means-setting-the-ison-attribute-flag-and-calling-the-fnwhntrnon-function-the-driving-concept-is-to-instantiate-a-mpbttn-that-generates-only-one-possible-ison-attribute-flag-true-readout-and-the-associated-function-execution-just-like-a-single-shot-trigger',1,'']]],
  ['to_20set_20a_20third_20signal_20on_20while_20the_20switch_20is_20off_118',['The &lt;strong&gt;Hinted Timer Latched&lt;/strong&gt;, or &lt;strong&gt;Staircase Timer Switch&lt;/strong&gt;, keeps the ON state since the moment the signal is debounced, and keeps the state during a set time, has the capability to give a warning when the service time is close to the end and the possibility to set a third signal ON while the switch is off.',['../index.html#the-hinted-timer-latched-or-staircase-timer-switch-keeps-the-on-state-since-the-moment-the-signal-is-debounced-and-keeps-the-state-during-a-set-time-has-the-capability-to-give-a-warning-when-the-service-time-is-close-to-the-end-and-the-possibility-to-set-a-third-signal-on-while-the-switch-is-off',1,'']]],
  ['to_20switches_20library_20buttontoswitch_119',['Buttons to Switches Library (ButtonToSwitch)',['../index.html',1,'']]],
  ['to_20the_20end_20and_20the_20possibility_20to_20set_20a_20third_20signal_20on_20while_20the_20switch_20is_20off_120',['The &lt;strong&gt;Hinted Timer Latched&lt;/strong&gt;, or &lt;strong&gt;Staircase Timer Switch&lt;/strong&gt;, keeps the ON state since the moment the signal is debounced, and keeps the state during a set time, has the capability to give a warning when the service time is close to the end and the possibility to set a third signal ON while the switch is off.',['../index.html#the-hinted-timer-latched-or-staircase-timer-switch-keeps-the-on-state-since-the-moment-the-signal-is-debounced-and-keeps-the-state-during-a-set-time-has-the-capability-to-give-a-warning-when-the-service-time-is-close-to-the-end-and-the-possibility-to-set-a-third-signal-on-while-the-switch-is-off',1,'']]],
  ['to_20the_20strong_20off_20state_20strong_121',['&lt;strong&gt;Latched DD-MPBs&lt;/strong&gt; are MPBs whose distinctive characteristic is that models switches that keep the ON state since the moment the input signal is stable (debouncing + Delay process), and keeps the ON state after the MPB is released and until an event un-latches them, setting them free to go back to the &lt;strong&gt;Off State&lt;/strong&gt;.',['../index.html#latched-dd-mpbs-are-mpbs-whose-distinctive-characteristic-is-that-models-switches-that-keep-the-on-state-since-the-moment-the-input-signal-is-stable-debouncing--delay-process-and-keeps-the-on-state-after-the-mpb-is-released-and-until-an-event-un-latches-them-setting-them-free-to-go-back-to-the-off-state',1,'']]],
  ['toggle_20strong_20a_20k_20a_20emergency_20latched_20keeps_20the_20on_20state_20since_20the_20moment_20the_20signal_20is_20debounced_20delayed_20and_20until_20an_20external_20signal_20is_20received_122',['The &lt;strong&gt;External released toggle&lt;/strong&gt; (a.k.a. Emergency latched), keeps the On state since the moment the signal is debounced &amp; delayed, and until an external signal is received.',['../index.html#the-external-released-toggle-aka-emergency-latched-keeps-the-on-state-since-the-moment-the-signal-is-debounced--delayed-and-until-an-external-signal-is-received',1,'']]],
  ['toggle_20switch_20strong_20keeps_20the_20on_20state_20since_20the_20moment_20the_20signal_20is_20stable_20debouncing_20delay_20process_20and_20keeps_20the_20on_20state_20after_20the_20push_20button_20is_20released_20and_20until_20it_20is_20pressed_20once_20again_123',['The &lt;strong&gt;Toggle switch&lt;/strong&gt;  keeps the ON state since the moment the signal is stable (debouncing + Delay process), and keeps the ON state after the push button is released and until it is pressed once again.',['../index.html#the-toggle-switch--keeps-the-on-state-since-the-moment-the-signal-is-stable-debouncing--delay-process-and-keeps-the-on-state-after-the-push-button-is-released-and-until-it-is-pressed-once-again',1,'']]],
  ['trigger_124',['The &lt;strong&gt;Single Service Voidable Momentary Push Button&lt;/strong&gt; keeps the &lt;strong&gt;On state&lt;/strong&gt; since the moment the signal is stable (debounce &amp; delay process) and until the moment the provided mechanisms implemented to be executed when the switch enters the &lt;strong&gt;On State&lt;/strong&gt; are started, that means setting the &lt;strong&gt;isOn&lt;/strong&gt; attribute flag and calling the &lt;strong&gt;fnWhnTrnOn&lt;/strong&gt; function. The driving concept is to instantiate a MPBttn that generates only one possible &lt;strong&gt;isOn&lt;/strong&gt; attribute flag true readout and the associated function execution, just like a single shot trigger.',['../index.html#the-single-service-voidable-momentary-push-button-keeps-the-on-state-since-the-moment-the-signal-is-stable-debounce--delay-process-and-until-the-moment-the-provided-mechanisms-implemented-to-be-executed-when-the-switch-enters-the-on-state-are-started-that-means-setting-the-ison-attribute-flag-and-calling-the-fnwhntrnon-function-the-driving-concept-is-to-instantiate-a-mpbttn-that-generates-only-one-possible-ison-attribute-flag-true-readout-and-the-associated-function-execution-just-like-a-single-shot-trigger',1,'']]],
  ['true_20of_20the_20instantiated_20objects_125',['The main output attribute flag kept updated for each and every class is the &lt;strong&gt;isOn&lt;/strong&gt; flag, which defines the &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Off State&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; (isOn=false) and the &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;On State&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; (isOn=true) of the instantiated objects.',['../index.html#the-main-output-attribute-flag-kept-updated-for-each-and-every-class-is-the-ison-flag-which-defines-the-_off-state_-isonfalse-and-the-_on-state_-isontrue-of-the-instantiated-objects',1,'']]],
  ['true_20readout_20and_20the_20associated_20function_20execution_20just_20like_20a_20single_20shot_20trigger_126',['The &lt;strong&gt;Single Service Voidable Momentary Push Button&lt;/strong&gt; keeps the &lt;strong&gt;On state&lt;/strong&gt; since the moment the signal is stable (debounce &amp; delay process) and until the moment the provided mechanisms implemented to be executed when the switch enters the &lt;strong&gt;On State&lt;/strong&gt; are started, that means setting the &lt;strong&gt;isOn&lt;/strong&gt; attribute flag and calling the &lt;strong&gt;fnWhnTrnOn&lt;/strong&gt; function. The driving concept is to instantiate a MPBttn that generates only one possible &lt;strong&gt;isOn&lt;/strong&gt; attribute flag true readout and the associated function execution, just like a single shot trigger.',['../index.html#the-single-service-voidable-momentary-push-button-keeps-the-on-state-since-the-moment-the-signal-is-stable-debounce--delay-process-and-until-the-moment-the-provided-mechanisms-implemented-to-be-executed-when-the-switch-enters-the-on-state-are-started-that-means-setting-the-ison-attribute-flag-and-calling-the-fnwhntrnon-function-the-driving-concept-is-to-instantiate-a-mpbttn-that-generates-only-one-possible-ison-attribute-flag-true-readout-and-the-associated-function-execution-just-like-a-single-shot-trigger',1,'']]]
